  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK896">
<l>eriyāṟ cuṭappaṭiṉu muyvuṇṭā muyyār</l>
<l>periyārp piḻaittoḻuku vār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though burnt by a fire (from a forest), one may perhaps live; (but) never will he live who has shown disrespect to the great (devotees).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
